chain.description: Question:  The `historical_for_fear_and_greed_index` API requires dates in "Year-Month-Day" format (e.g., "2022-06-01"). Also, the API only returns the index score; it doesn't provide a separate "rating."  Do you still want to proceed with fetching just the index scores for those dates?
